  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=426e3776&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFGB4hYw9Fec06ickVGQB5Yva2X0EUep5bhQhiaR2txpMjErGrpVkzCQnLicV1gejIyH46K46jNBicb03yNibvQMLPau9JY2UibbhB6bmuBtT4RYOE%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p>给你的虾装上扣子罗盘Trace，从此告别黑箱操作，让每一步都看得见！</p>\n  <div style=\"padding:0px 15px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:2px;font-size:14px;line-height:2.2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100000081\" data-ratio=\"0.18888888888888888\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f4b98e83&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYXg9pjicEkwmic0e7v17KjINPyh8YWFGwHRxOEZ0Z6IIs1CBrX5I9uQ8DxpDIuQMtXswpltmQbepFwRG3WJ3js8eGI9oPThXJEVt4z5gIvR7g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D1\"></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">最近很多朋友部署了OpenClaw，让虾来查资料、写代码、回消息...在解锁全新体验的同时，你可能也会遇到这些崩溃时刻：</span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding-top:4px;margin:1em 0;text-indent:0;border-left:3px solid #DBDBDB;padding-left:10px;font-size:15px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">“我让它查个航班，它说搞定了，结果完全是编的——到底哪步出了问题？”</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">“一次对话烧了格外多的Token，但我不知道贵在哪...”</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">“虾能自动执行任务，但它到底执行了哪些，我还不清楚。”</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就是很多“养虾人”的现状：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">它有点像个黑箱，你喂它API Key和钱，它像扎进水底一样去运行，你很难清清楚楚看明白它在干嘛…</span></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100000078\" data-ratio=\"0.18888888888888888\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f886ec56&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYXg9pjicEkwniaGb0yd9HjHMOGFunFW1sr8vWdjrBDUsSUz2CNicrxZOhrpn4TuvjgVsBcAHlMNuUHhj7RUhXT3d1ne30UHUxb14eCjQowMIW4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D2\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">扣子罗盘 Trace 现在支持 OpenClaw 集成了！无论你的虾部署在哪里，都能给它装上一台行车记录仪</span><span data-eleid=\"16\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;—— 做了什么、走了哪步，全都有迹可循。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span data-eleid=\"16\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">从用户请求输入，到 OpenClaw 处理、模型推理、工具调用、最终输出，每一步都被记录、可回放：</span></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100000070\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=89ca99ca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYXg9pjicEkwmSbwWOr4pumr8rqbqVqY2ia1pyz6YLmJzVB1Jm8SqOBfV1sSk8LGEMCP8n4tFtfQsJZnXRVuMOxNncSwnbP3PJXtvaQumXltRs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D3\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这样，你的虾将“不再是黑的”，运行轨迹从水下黑箱来到了你的视野中，</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2.2;padding: 0px 15px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">OpenClaw</span></span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2.2;padding: 0px 15px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的每一次运行，都会像</span></span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2.2;padding: 0px 15px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">行车记录仪一样——全程可视、可追溯、可优化。</span></span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100000055\" data-ratio=\"0.5037037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a4289686&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYXg9pjicEkwl5yBnTSS0Bh2bjRFRTc9J3KaIicBfuayibdQHQJzHouxe9N1jic1LdANaV5EcbAItn0ib9iaCGQwdeoVKx3JHuBB6lPowoia042Bld4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D4\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.18888888888888888\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100000054\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1b328a4a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYXg9pjicEkwl2XBbia3T0sxajDR8woBmMOULZVwyS24lsYtA96LDZKq1wnzes1z418Y4xnxwO1MPiaQTQ7wmOv4ru6SAYgHrzicPFhaFAQqqSTk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D5\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">@老王，OpenClaw 重度用户，部署了3只🦞处理日常任务。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">上周吐槽：“一条对话怎么烧了20000多Token？”</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">打开 Trace 一查，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 2.2;font-style: normal;text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;box-sizing: border-box;\">虾</span><span style=\"line-height: 2.2;font-style: normal;text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;box-sizing: border-box;\">的运</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">行链路全暴露了：</span></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding-top:4px;margin:1em 0;text-indent:0;border-left:3px solid #DBDBDB;padding-left:10px;font-size:15px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">第一轮推理：系统提示词太啰嗦，占了8000 Token</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">第二轮：上下文没裁剪，把前面10轮对话全带上，12000 Token</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">第三轮：OpenClaw 调用的搜索工具返回了一大段HTML，又吞了6000 Token实际有用信息：不到10%</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">老王：“我差点把🦞炖了…”</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">优化后：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">同样的OpenClaw，同样效果，Token降到原来的1/5。</span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就是 Trace + OpenClaw 的魔力：成本黑洞变透明，让你的优化有方向。</span></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.18888888888888888\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-imgfileid=\"100000059\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4f44bc7e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYXg9pjicEkwkN8JD0PFSgEehYETGiaM4iaCMT7P1tzkbDbicQibLicLzCLvmiakRBHNdnYWSambKcjsRDhbrlRCzUZueAiae6OdbpG484rPS5DJ7SfY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D6\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">当你在让🦞工作时，如果遇到这些情况，建议现在就打开Trace来查一查！可能在某个被遗忘的角落，隐藏着“吞token黑洞”…</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;box-sizing: border-box;\">1、输出了离谱答案</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">【以前】猜原因，调提示词碰运气，调一晚上还是不知道哪错了…</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">【现在】打开扣子罗盘 Trace，完整推理链路一目了然——哪步上下文跑偏了，一眼就能定位，5分钟修完。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;box-sizing: border-box;\">2、工具调用忽然挂了</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">【以前】等它恢复，然后就没有然后了，问题复现全靠缘分。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">【现在】用Trace 看工具调用的入参、返回值、报错信息全记录，哪一步出问题清清楚楚。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;box-sizing: border-box;\">3、这条对话好贵</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">【以前】20000 Token 就这么没了？不知道贵在哪，只能干瞪眼。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">【现在】Trace 把每一步 Token 消耗拆开，找到消耗大头精准优化。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;box-sizing: border-box;\">4、OpenClaw 突然变笨</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">【以前】换模型、调参数，折腾一圈发现还是无解。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">【现在】看上下文演进，是不是历史信息污染，问题根因一查就知。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;box-sizing: border-box;\">5、响应慢得像蜗牛</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">【以前】不知道慢在哪，只能瞎猜是网络问题还是模型问题。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">【现在】各节点耗时一目了然，精准定位性能瓶颈，优化有方向。</span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">当你给🦞装上</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2.2;padding: 0px 15px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.8px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;}]\">扣子罗盘 Trace这个</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;secti